Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与第二月亮对接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用其动力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度发射迪格玛Xenon炮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 战场情况混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在发射不免殃及友军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为实现计划 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不惜付出任何牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我说得办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉·格拉密斯 准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉·格拉密斯开始变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人描绘的伊甸蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓将其化为现实
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTA-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续前进 沿途支援友军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破当前宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔纳森 不许哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让队长的牺牲白费吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击溃维甘阵线！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后备动力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就用上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 我知道你很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除维生系统外 停止其他系统供应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力维持最大航速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士队 迎击侧方来敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与敌人陷入混战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看准了是敌人再打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达孜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手下的将士们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你皆有相同的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坚信自己脚下的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你创建伊甸的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是你发自内心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么了 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西尔哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子不惜大义灭亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成 因为这点事就缩了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无路可退…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有通向伊甸之路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人 有何吩咐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆 把高达引到迪格玛Xenon炮的射线轴上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天神号一道 一举歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同高达…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他们的突进企图 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扼杀联邦的胜机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这场战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 杰哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊尔 我去引出高达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白这个命令意味着什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从这个命令 就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少记住那些阵亡者的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样善良体贴的杰哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想像过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们即将营造的 伊甸中的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸是 他的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最重要的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人就能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做回那个体贴善良的杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了保护他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护他善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测系统反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方路线上出现敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右满舵 避让
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人突然发什么神经？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄恩 我会阻止这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 进笼子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡之笼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达 要不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用来结束战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 锥炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你坏杰哈特大人的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开 臭海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊尔 你不该来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早有心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 雷伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种恐怖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即呼叫奥克拉姆德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回答 再次呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底打得什么算盘 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们又要使用要塞炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种武器不是不可能短时间连射吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢在战场上进行那种变形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中必有缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦格雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要塞会不会从第二月亮获取能量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为光束炮充能？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅从热感器上观察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法排除这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 乱战情况下发射…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算以自己人为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走高达和天神号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记 对手是维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么立即下令避让
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 天神号只要继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会盯住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以天神号为饵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让其他舰艇离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲自己人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特他竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起 天神号乘员集体离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 离开天神号？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下 出去也会被敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在这里也是被打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经要求他们营救撤离的乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营救？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 准备撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即前往第三格纳库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-1 Gransa 出击
