Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘员马上就要离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引敌人火力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃天神号？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱特 乔纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来迟了 明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就这样跳进宇宙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令说不要上逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在甲板待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们上海盗船？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别指望敌人的探测器是瞎子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 登上海盗船巴洛诺克号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伙计 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家抓紧DarkHunter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超级推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气离开敌人的射线轴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪里也别想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到最后一刻不许离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以免敌人察觉我们的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这种…被这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 看我为你报仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家抓住DarkHunter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱特先生 请快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不放过它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 杂兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再垂死挣扎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级推进器准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火倒计时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 点火同时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也用最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只当辅助推进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要…活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能来找你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台高达全部在射程范围以内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆 芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道道歉也无法得到原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让计划成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒的在天之灵安息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再提哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够… 在您手下战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最大的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙拉姆 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让伊甸 回到我们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要踏上伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特 你这该死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军战舰 击沉5艘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲了自己最忠诚的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有不成之理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底…在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底干了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想胜过我这个哥哥 不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要击落高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢下这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人从法·扎德上出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特 不惜牺牲部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要实现夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已经放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人性的大义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何价值可言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂个屁！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸不是为了让人活得更有人样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为伊甸献出了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切…都在逝去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…握不住它…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有把握不住的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多次放走我这个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明作为战士之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你首先是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人的…夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的…梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则… 我们是为何而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们度过的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士社团的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段时光是何等的充实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定…嫉妒过我的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…想与爱人生儿育女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你那样…生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 这下可以优胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 太厉害了杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次多亏你 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有你才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你才有现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特！
